       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6BO04.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DECLARATION.
           05  WS-CAPITAL-INTEREST   PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-CLASSIFICATION     PIC X(8) VALUE 'NONOWNER'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-CAPITAL-INTEREST
           PERFORM 2300-CLASSIFY-PARTNER
           DISPLAY WS-CLASSIFICATION
           STOP RUN.
       2300-CLASSIFY-PARTNER.
           EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN WS-CAPITAL-INTEREST > 15
                 MOVE 'OWNER' TO WS-CLASSIFICATION
              WHEN OTHER
                 MOVE 'NONOWNER' TO WS-CLASSIFICATION
           END-EVALUATE.
